{"tid":322811,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"應該繼續做 定讀master?","createTime":"2017-07-15T06:36:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-16T17:01:57.000Z","uid":105709,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4aa3dfdbd054388fcb8aaf60ae957337f4f5f9ff","tid":322811,"uid":105709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T06:36:30.000Z","msg":"先講下自己背景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n三大sicence grad 讀緊書時發現對航空業有興趣 <br />\n所以grad左之後就入左去做 雖然唔算係好中意份工 但都叫有啲關係<br />\n<br />\n一直以來都想讀番個航空管理master 希望第時有多啲出路 甚至入民航處做<br />\n但由於本科唔係同科 加上under grad得2.2 所以得英國一間雞雞地嘅學店俾左offer我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叫做好過冇啦<br />\n<br />\n同一時間 機緣巧合之下 又有航空公司搵我interview<br />\n個人對呢份工有興趣 而且都知道自己會中意呢份工<br />\n不過都知道career path唔係特別secure<br />\n<br />\n問題嚟喇<br />\n而家有幾個option<br />\n<br />\n1. 去讀master 番嚟再搵工:<br />\naim就aim入民航處 不過如果入唔到都係要做番airline嘅officer工<br />\n再者間uni唔係特別top 所以有啲顧慮<br />\n<br />\n2. 番新工 睇下前路點再決定讀唔讀番書:<br />\n不過讀書應該趁早讀?<br />\n<br />\n3. 番新工 同時間讀online master:<br />\n同on campus master比較 online冇得出國 見識冇咁廣闊<br />\n而且可能有啲HR覺得online master冇認受性 (我估?)<br />\n<br />\n最後 其實我嘅目標係入民航處 或者airline管理層<br />\n政府工好似有個master會好啲<br />\nairline升上去我估都係睇機遇 睇彩數<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d77483fb7a04ba98bf9583bd6ee122827ae76e99","tid":322811,"uid":105709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T06:49:12.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ee56bdeed438b00cccaed631713119529f74970","tid":322811,"uid":13020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T07:02:53.000Z","msg":"巴打咩年紀？ 做左野幾耐"},{"pid":"a97a9d43f6677647f37b63920a8831b2a8c69776","tid":322811,"uid":5067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T07:03:47.000Z","msg":"番工再上online course<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":