762154d27ae78fd046b6bb98aa415683259ab417","tid":322811,"uid":105709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T07:18:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>返過工好難再full time讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3rd option<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nPart Time讀書啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不過同類型科目得online course<br />\n點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f3808af899f316e25cd975baf70a012bce3eb7e","tid":322811,"uid":105709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T07:21:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打咩年紀？ 做左野幾耐</blockquote><br />\n23歲 做左年半多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真後生，咁快做左年半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該話 今年24 不過未過生日啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過都真係想趁後生 如果要讀就嗱嗱臨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1445eb90784297ede82c920131ec98db5c5dfeae","tid":322811,"uid":3548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T09:24:56.000Z","msg":"邊間雞u?"},{"pid":"f6d54bc508c89524e48b14f25e0eb9f32a99d2ea","tid":322811,"uid":105709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T10:07:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊間雞u?</blockquote><br />\nCoventry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dffe42f31844b85e526eca3cfade0bb95c6b3856","tid":322811,"uid":105121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T11:53:07.000Z","msg":"人工?"},{"pid":"7c59d6b3c53cac1d08ee0b1c6fff2557b53cb6ef","tid":322811,"uid":105709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T12:00:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人工?</blockquote><br />\n15k啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n機場工都冇乜好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11e4a9d6952cb9050fc1442c3f6b13b220785ff1","tid":322811,"uid":75692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T13:28:23.000Z","msg":"廢過三大唔好讀"},{"pid":"e2e759b276318e49c7eaf27d8a0334ba5d7dbe36","tid":322811,"uid":125087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T16:12:11.000Z","msg":"巴打有冇俾之前國泰炒人單嘢嚇倒？"},{"pid":"e3df5779add00d89580ae74dc89dbd8ac90a70d8","tid":322811,"uid":105709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T20:58:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打有冇俾之前國泰炒人單嘢嚇倒？</blockquote><br />\n咁又冇喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反正真係有能力嘅去邊都得<br />\n<br />\n不過首先要有人俾機會你展現你嘅能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac94bc5d4b440b2cdfa5bd40a937f2f38f580c9d","tid":322811,"uid":82040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T15:22:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打有冇俾之前國泰炒人單嘢嚇倒？</blockquote><br />\n咁又冇喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反正真係有能力嘅去邊都得<br />\n<br />\n不過首先要有人俾機會你展現你嘅能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nX2<br />\n去第間airlines都得架姐"},{"pid":"f3602835873ccb50b8d97a505946b204b27ff48c","tid":322811,"uid":67867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T16:46:19.000Z","msg":"航空業既咩field先<br />\n讀aviation management係咪真係會幫到你上管理層呀"},{"pid":"b232abdbe4062260d2a7907e4e48190cbc88bad4","tid":322811,"uid":105709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T17:01:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>航空業既咩field先<br />\n讀aviation management係咪真係會幫到你上管理層呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你嘅意思係我做緊咩field?<br />\n定我想入咩field?<br />\n<br />\n希望啦<br />\n最想入CAD<br />\nAviation analyst/consultant都有興趣<br />\n<br />\n如果想做analyst/consultant我諗有個master大機會好多 <br />\n始終undergrad唔係讀呢範 入行難好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}